## Purified Talc; Talcum

Talc is a powdered, selected natural hydrated magnesium silicate. It may contain varying amounts of aluminium and iron in forms insoluble in 1M sulphuric acid.

Category: Pharmaceutical aid (dusting powder).

Solubility: Practically insoluble in water and in dilute solutions of acids and alkali hydroxides.

